Manage Your Omni-Channel Work While On the Go

With Omni Inbox in Salesforce Mobile, work from anywhere using your mobile device.

Set Up Omni-Channel on Your Mobile Device
To use Omni Inbox in the Salesforce Mobile app, you must have the Digital Engagement license. To set up Omni Inbox, complete these tasks.
Manage Work with Omni Inbox
To accept new work and resume previously assigned work, open Omni Inbox in the Salesforce Mobile app.
title: Setting Up Omni-Channel on Mobile Device
